Hi, here's a little about myself;
I'm 35(but look younger, and have been told I'm g.l), caucasian, about 5'11,170 lbs, dark brown hair with some reddish and gray, and hazel eyes.I've never been married and have no children, or drama in my life.I'm a non smoker, and don't drink or use drugs.I'm a Christian, and God is number one in my life.I live with my elderly parents (who are both in poor health) by choice.I work nights at a decent job, that I've been at for the last three years, I'm hardworking and reliable.I own a good vehicle.I'm a very caring and giving person, with a big heart.I'm shy and reserved.
I'm looking for a woman who wants a committed relationship-I'm too old for games, please don't waste my time.It would be great to meet someone who would like to go to church together.If you'd like to get to know me, feel free to send a message, and please include a pic, I have some to share.Use your favorite color as subject.Thank you for reading my post.
